The '''Mynock Hole''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] in [[Vlarnya]] on [[Courkrus]]. It was the hideout of the [[Blackstar Pirates]], provided [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]], and both [[Gender/Legends|male]] and female [[Prostitute/Legends|prostitutes]] in a restricted back area.

